skinname-continuum: เวกเตอร์แบบเก่า (2553)
continuum-skin-desc:
Provides 2 Continuum skins:
* 11 - The Modern version of MonoBook with fresh look and many usability improvements.
*  - The Continuum built as part of the WMF [[mw:Desktop Improvements]] project.
